  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable, DomainObject

    public class DomainInnerNode
extends DomainInnerNode_Base
    InnerNode specialized to hold Oids as Keys. The serialization of DomainInnerNode is done using a JSON object, containing the External Id of the key objects, and the external id of the AbstractNode.

      • externalizeOidIndexedMap

        public static String externalizeOidIndexedMap(TreeMap map)
        Serializes the given map to a JSON object containing a mapping between the External Ids of the Key and Value objects. Uses BPlusTree.LAST_KEY_REPRESENTATION as a well-known value to represent the Last Key.
        Parameters:
        map - Map to serialize. Must be in the form [Oid, AbstractNode]
        Returns:
        A JSON Object containing the mapping
